1.2.name: wordpress/get-snarky
1.2.description: This is a fork / modification of the original 'Hello Dolly' plugin. Only instead of those quotes, I've included random funny quotes (mainly from twitter). Clearly not earth-shattering, but fun none the less. Please note that the original 'Hello Dolly' plugin is not required (or encouraged, for that matter).
